!!!
%html
%head
	%title= yield (:title)
	= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true
	= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true
	= csrf_meta_tags

%body
	%nav.navbar.navbar-default
		.container
			.navbar-brand Anziel
			%ul.nav.navbar-nav
				%li= link_to "All Jobs", root_path
				- Category.all.each do |category|
					%li= link_to category.name, jobs_path(category: category.name)
			.navbar-text.navbar-right.navbar-link To make a New Job Posting: <iframe src="http://www.paywithatweet.com/dlbutton01.php?id=aaf0b8f0-5e6a-455e-b66b-16a8e391939e" class="br-right-md" name="paytweet_button" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" height="24px" width="145px"></iframe>
			
	.container
		.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3		
			= yield
